FBIS3-16335 "drsov051_v_94007" FBIS-SOV-94-051 Document Type:Daily Report 15 Mar 1994 Lithuania Travel Documents for Stateless Persons Planned WS1603122194 Vilnius ELTA in Lithuanian 1252 GMT 15 Mar 94 WS1603122194 Vilnius ELTA Language: Lithuanian Article Type:BFN [Text] It has been two weeks since Lithuania began to receive applications from individuals wishing to acquire a "Travel Document of a Stateless Person." Persons who are Lithuania's permanent residents, but who have no Lithuanian or any other citizenship, require this document when travelling abroad. The Migration Department has reported to ELTA that only 123 people submitted applications throughout Lithuania over the first 14 days.
